Name: Aim Master
About the game: Aim Master is the FPS/TPS aim training game, developed to improve your aiming skills in the famous battle royal FPS/TPS game. Features: - Mouse sensitivity same with the famous battle royal FPS/TPS game. - 4 Assult Rifles and 1 Sniper rifle provided. - Holographic sight, Red dot sight, 2x scope, 3x scope, 4x scope, 6x scope - Very similar gun recoil pattern with PUBG
